WEBVTT

01:37.780 --> 01:40.759
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.350 --> 01:43.620
[Episode 21]

01:44.789 --> 01:46.720
Yaoniang, why aren't you dancing?

01:47.039 --> 01:49.200
Dance! Dance! Dance!

01:49.350 --> 01:51.200
Hurry up and dance! Dance!

01:51.350 --> 01:53.280
Dance! Dance!

01:53.509 --> 01:53.920
Sir.

01:53.920 --> 01:54.400
Yeah!

01:54.400 --> 01:55.729
Why aren't you dancing?

01:55.840 --> 01:56.350
No need.

01:56.350 --> 01:57.430
Hurry up and dance, Yaoniang!

01:57.430 --> 01:58.490
Hurry up and dance!

01:58.509 --> 01:59.039
Yeah!

01:59.200 --> 02:00.430
Dance! Dance!

02:32.960 --> 02:35.090
Why is the lady I was just drinking with

02:35.360 --> 02:37.030
dancing up there?

03:10.240 --> 03:10.710
Nice...

03:17.150 --> 03:18.280
She's not Yaoniang.

03:20.000 --> 03:20.680
Oh no.

03:21.710 --> 03:23.310
Yaoniang must have run away.

03:23.520 --> 03:24.180
Go find her!

03:24.630 --> 03:25.150
Okay.

03:27.190 --> 03:27.910
I offer

03:28.400 --> 03:29.310
5,000 taels

03:29.840 --> 03:30.840
to have this lady

03:31.190 --> 03:32.079
drink with me!

03:34.310 --> 03:35.750
Sir, you've got good taste!

03:35.750 --> 03:36.490
Yaoniang

03:36.740 --> 03:38.000
doesn't just dance well.

03:38.000 --> 03:38.630
She can really

03:38.630 --> 03:40.310
hold her liquor too!

04:28.760 --> 04:29.750
Romantic love

04:30.390 --> 04:31.850
is stronger than diamond.

04:32.180 --> 04:32.840
Wonderful.

04:33.240 --> 04:34.270
Wonderful!

04:48.740 --> 04:51.190
[Tianxiang Restaurant]

04:57.310 --> 04:58.240
Why are you here?

05:00.510 --> 05:01.070
Just now...

05:01.070 --> 05:01.970
After you left,

05:02.190 --> 05:03.430
my condition worsened

05:03.430 --> 05:04.360
and I passed out.

05:05.140 --> 05:06.430
The owner here found me

05:07.120 --> 05:08.250
and brought me back.

05:08.600 --> 05:09.260
Just now...

05:10.000 --> 05:11.270
I had a bit to drink,

05:11.750 --> 05:12.480
so they mistook me

05:12.480 --> 05:13.600
for one of the dancers here

05:13.600 --> 05:15.040
and pushed me onto the stage.

05:15.040 --> 05:17.100
An immortal sect cultivator like you

05:17.360 --> 05:19.800
got caught and brought
to Tianxiang Restaurant?

05:19.800 --> 05:20.390
Yeah.

05:20.830 --> 05:22.160
I'm stupid and unlucky.

05:22.160 --> 05:22.750
No matter where I go,

05:22.750 --> 05:24.240
I get bullied and made a fool of.

05:24.240 --> 05:25.900
Didn't you already know that?

05:32.800 --> 05:33.860
What are you doing?

05:33.870 --> 05:34.920
Checking your pulse.

05:34.920 --> 05:35.480
No need!

05:45.270 --> 05:46.920
There's nothing seriously wrong with you.

05:46.920 --> 05:47.850
If you rest well,

05:48.070 --> 05:49.200
you'll be fine soon.

05:58.310 --> 05:59.570
What's your next move?

06:00.950 --> 06:01.680
My next move?

06:03.190 --> 06:04.040
I have no idea.

06:05.310 --> 06:07.570
Are you going back to the Central Plains?

06:08.270 --> 06:10.070
My junior sister left me a letter

06:10.560 --> 06:12.270
and took off without saying goodbye.

06:12.270 --> 06:13.310
I've sent my spirit bird

06:13.310 --> 06:14.070
to find her.

06:14.390 --> 06:16.250
I have to wait for her to come back.

06:21.000 --> 06:21.800
How's...

06:22.310 --> 06:23.120
your injury?

06:23.680 --> 06:24.240
Injury?

06:25.200 --> 06:25.710
There.

06:29.680 --> 06:31.080
It healed a long time ago.

06:31.310 --> 06:32.000
You know that

06:32.000 --> 06:32.720
about me.

06:33.190 --> 06:34.990
I could survive a thousand cuts.

06:35.070 --> 06:36.750
This is nothing.

06:42.950 --> 06:43.720
Lu Qianqiao.

06:45.390 --> 06:46.590
Among the War Demons,

06:47.510 --> 06:49.510
there must be some good ones, right?

06:53.800 --> 06:54.630
Maybe.

06:55.630 --> 06:58.230
The immortal sect
has heretical cultivators.

06:58.270 --> 06:59.830
The Human Race has villains.

06:59.830 --> 07:01.040
So there are probably some good people

07:01.040 --> 07:02.270
among the War Demons.

07:06.510 --> 07:07.190
Xin Mei.

07:08.480 --> 07:09.610
I'm not a bad person.

07:10.120 --> 07:11.310
I'm a War Demon,

07:11.830 --> 07:13.690
but I grew up among the Human Race.

07:13.830 --> 07:14.920
I never took part

07:14.950 --> 07:16.150
in that war back then.

07:19.120 --> 07:20.520
Yes, I've killed people.

07:20.630 --> 07:21.800
But only villains.

07:22.510 --> 07:24.510
I've served in the Human Race's army

07:24.720 --> 07:26.450
and worked as a minor official.

07:26.560 --> 07:28.040
I have a clear conscience.

07:28.680 --> 07:30.740
No matter how unfairly I was treated,

07:30.770 --> 07:31.530
I have never

07:31.560 --> 07:32.690
killed an innocent.

07:37.040 --> 07:37.630
I know.

07:38.240 --> 07:40.040
I shouldn't be telling you this,

07:40.240 --> 07:42.270
but I don't want you to misunderstand me

07:42.270 --> 07:42.920
or hate me.

07:46.630 --> 07:47.830
I just don't know

07:47.830 --> 07:48.920
how to face you.

07:52.360 --> 07:53.430
You're a War Demon,

07:54.560 --> 07:56.020
the sworn enemy of my kind.

07:57.190 --> 07:58.310
You've lied to me,

07:59.560 --> 08:00.960
but you've also saved me.

08:02.510 --> 08:04.750
So I really don't know...

08:18.070 --> 08:18.680
I'm sorry.

08:24.920 --> 08:25.680
Lu Qianqiao.

08:27.600 --> 08:29.330
Are you really not a bad person?

08:29.430 --> 08:30.560
I'm not a bad person.

08:31.430 --> 08:32.630
Can you promise that?

08:33.120 --> 08:33.789
I promise.

09:01.840 --> 09:03.100
Get some good rest now.

09:03.270 --> 09:04.240
As soon as day breaks,

09:04.240 --> 09:06.100
we'll find another place to stay.

09:07.200 --> 09:07.930
Lu Qianqiao.

09:10.840 --> 09:12.240
There are still some things

09:12.240 --> 09:13.500
I haven't figured out.

09:14.030 --> 09:14.750
Besides,

09:14.870 --> 09:17.120
I need to wait for my junior
in North Xiang.

09:17.120 --> 09:17.960
So for now,

09:18.120 --> 09:19.870
I won't be returning
to the Central Plains.

09:19.870 --> 09:20.320
Okay.

09:21.120 --> 09:21.920
I understand.

09:22.910 --> 09:23.510
Also,

09:24.240 --> 09:26.200
I've been to Qinghong Sect's

09:26.480 --> 09:27.870
Bishui Branch in Xutuo City.

09:27.870 --> 09:28.720
I've also met the boss

09:28.720 --> 09:29.920
of the camel caravan,

09:30.150 --> 09:31.510
Lord Song of Wei County,

09:31.960 --> 09:33.790
and the landlady of Safe Haven Inn.

09:33.790 --> 09:34.360
On top of that,

09:34.360 --> 09:36.510
there was the time
I went up against Xia Xuanzi.

09:36.510 --> 09:37.710
No matter who you are,

09:38.600 --> 09:40.120
you're my savior.

09:40.840 --> 09:41.900
I owe you my thanks.

09:45.440 --> 09:46.370
You're welcome.

10:13.840 --> 10:14.640
What's wrong?

10:16.670 --> 10:17.440
I've been

10:18.080 --> 10:19.540
feeling a bit weak lately.

10:23.000 --> 10:24.130
I need to find a place

10:24.440 --> 10:26.240
to go into seclusion for a while.

10:26.390 --> 10:27.590
For the next few days,

10:27.750 --> 10:29.010
take care of yourself.

10:29.320 --> 10:30.450
If you're in danger,

10:30.630 --> 10:31.390
just run.

10:31.960 --> 10:32.820
Don't force it.

10:35.200 --> 10:35.960
I know.

10:37.240 --> 10:38.440
You take care too.

10:41.320 --> 10:41.870
I'm off.

11:08.150 --> 11:09.600
I know I was wrong.

11:09.790 --> 11:10.510
Please.

11:10.790 --> 11:11.630
Please!

11:12.510 --> 11:13.510
I know I was wrong!

11:13.550 --> 11:14.870
Here in Qianyan Cave,

11:16.000 --> 11:17.320
we're all family.

11:19.630 --> 11:21.150
Even though he went a little too far

11:21.150 --> 11:22.030
joking around,

11:22.630 --> 11:25.120
there's no reason to kill him.

11:36.960 --> 11:37.390
No.

11:38.840 --> 11:39.500
I was wrong.

11:39.840 --> 11:41.100
I'll never do it again.

11:43.440 --> 11:44.120
I was wrong.

11:44.630 --> 11:45.320
I was wrong.

11:47.360 --> 11:47.840
Sheng.

11:50.180 --> 11:50.880
I was wrong.

11:50.910 --> 11:51.360
Sheng.

11:51.750 --> 11:52.510
Please.

11:52.670 --> 11:53.130
Wake up.

11:53.390 --> 11:53.920
Let me go.

11:54.240 --> 11:54.670
Let me go.

11:54.670 --> 11:55.080
Sheng.

11:55.550 --> 11:56.030
Sheng.

11:56.910 --> 11:57.510
Wake up.

11:58.240 --> 11:59.840
No!

12:11.240 --> 12:11.910
It's okay.

12:17.600 --> 12:18.200
It's okay.

12:34.910 --> 12:37.150
Since you said Yaoniang has already left,

12:37.150 --> 12:38.200
then there's no need for us

12:38.200 --> 12:39.530
to look for her anymore.

12:41.000 --> 12:41.930
Sha Sanxing said

12:42.480 --> 12:43.760
the dancer he was close to

12:43.760 --> 12:44.880
once told him that

12:45.600 --> 12:47.460
on that day, she was blindfolded,

12:47.790 --> 12:48.600
put on a camel,

12:49.080 --> 12:50.840
and taken west for three days.

12:52.200 --> 12:52.670
Look.

12:53.870 --> 12:54.790
West of Phoenix City,

12:54.790 --> 12:56.520
there are three stops in total.

12:56.790 --> 12:57.520
The first one

12:57.750 --> 12:59.550
is Wushuang City in North Xiang.

13:00.120 --> 13:00.910
It's a place

13:00.910 --> 13:02.270
with all kinds of people.

13:02.270 --> 13:03.480
Lots of shady deals

13:03.550 --> 13:04.550
go on here.

13:05.630 --> 13:06.430
The second one

13:06.440 --> 13:07.300
is Baibu Slope.

13:07.750 --> 13:09.550
It's mainly a stop for caravans.

13:09.670 --> 13:10.720
Most of the long-term residents here

13:10.720 --> 13:12.630
are merchants doing business.

13:13.720 --> 13:14.450
The third one

13:14.630 --> 13:15.560
is Qianyan Cave.

13:16.150 --> 13:16.880
Qianyan Cave

13:17.080 --> 13:19.010
seems to be a place of cultivation.

13:19.120 --> 13:20.320
It's quite isolated,

13:20.390 --> 13:22.520
so we can't get much information on it.

13:22.720 --> 13:24.580
Why do you want to know about this?

13:26.510 --> 13:28.640
I came to North Xiang to renew my blood.

13:29.480 --> 13:30.120
I know.

13:30.480 --> 13:31.880
You want to become human.

13:32.430 --> 13:32.910
Yes.

13:34.000 --> 13:36.150
But as I renew my bones, my blood,

13:36.630 --> 13:37.360
and my heart,

13:37.550 --> 13:39.880
my Cultivation will drop significantly.

13:40.000 --> 13:41.270
After I finish renewing my blood,

13:41.270 --> 13:43.080
I'll be at
the Foundation Establishment Stage.

13:43.080 --> 13:45.140
I won't be able to defeat anyone then.

13:45.320 --> 13:45.870
So,

13:46.320 --> 13:47.650
before I renew my blood,

13:47.870 --> 13:50.150
I have to eliminate that young cultivator.

13:50.150 --> 13:51.010
But that person

13:51.200 --> 13:53.260
has probably reached the Void Stage.

13:53.630 --> 13:55.200
Even without the blood renewal,

13:55.200 --> 13:56.660
you can't beat him, right?

13:57.360 --> 13:58.550
I fell from above

13:58.550 --> 13:59.150
after all.

13:59.550 --> 14:01.030
I still have all the techniques
I should have.

14:01.030 --> 14:01.840
Don't worry.

14:03.240 --> 14:04.840
After a few more days of rest,

14:04.960 --> 14:07.090
I'll go to these three places one by one

14:07.120 --> 14:08.150
and find him out.

14:09.790 --> 14:11.030
Noodles are here!

14:20.150 --> 14:21.350
I'll go with you then.

14:21.840 --> 14:22.320
No.

14:22.550 --> 14:23.510
It's too dangerous.

14:23.510 --> 14:24.470
That's exactly

14:24.750 --> 14:25.720
why I have to go.

14:26.200 --> 14:27.480
This is the trouble I caused.

14:27.480 --> 14:28.940
I have to handle it myself.

14:29.120 --> 14:29.850
This trouble

14:30.000 --> 14:31.460
was caused by me after all.

14:32.430 --> 14:34.360
That's why I didn't refuse your help.

14:34.360 --> 14:36.160
But I still have to do something.

14:36.440 --> 14:37.500
It's settled then.

14:44.790 --> 14:45.390
By the way,

14:45.960 --> 14:47.750
when can you help me

14:47.910 --> 14:49.310
fully restore my memory?

14:50.600 --> 14:52.720
Your memory was erased by Chu Ying.

14:53.240 --> 14:54.040
He's not here,

14:54.200 --> 14:55.630
so there's nothing I can do.

14:55.630 --> 14:56.550
Chu Ying?

14:57.720 --> 14:58.960
Is he the senior who helped bring you back

14:58.960 --> 15:00.760
from Chongling Valley that day?

15:01.240 --> 15:01.750
Yes.

15:02.360 --> 15:04.030
But he's not from Chongling Valley.

15:04.030 --> 15:05.200
His best technique

15:05.360 --> 15:06.550
is Ghost Covering Eyes.

15:06.550 --> 15:08.210
It can erase anyone's memory.

15:08.550 --> 15:09.240
But he has

15:09.240 --> 15:10.840
some physical problems now.

15:10.840 --> 15:12.120
So he found a safe place

15:12.240 --> 15:13.870
and went into seclusion to cultivate.

15:13.870 --> 15:15.000
When will he be back?

15:16.630 --> 15:17.480
I don't know.

15:24.720 --> 15:25.390
Attendant.

15:25.390 --> 15:25.980
Look at him.

15:25.980 --> 15:26.870
He doesn't even look like a good person.

15:26.870 --> 15:28.000
If Master Zhou

15:28.000 --> 15:28.660
comes back,

15:28.670 --> 15:29.730
please let me know.

15:30.200 --> 15:31.780
My house is on the left side
of Pilin Alley.

15:31.780 --> 15:32.430
It's the third one.

15:32.430 --> 15:33.000
Will do.

15:33.910 --> 15:35.320
But to be honest,

15:35.720 --> 15:36.550
Master Zhou

15:36.550 --> 15:37.950
is a traveling merchant.

15:38.030 --> 15:40.030
He only comes to restock once a year.

15:40.390 --> 15:41.320
I'm afraid

15:41.550 --> 15:43.200
you won't be seeing him anytime soon.

15:43.200 --> 15:44.930
Please don't get your hopes up.

15:53.480 --> 15:55.120
How dare you sell the painting?

15:55.120 --> 15:55.910
Do you know

15:55.910 --> 15:57.030
how important it is?

15:57.030 --> 15:57.560
Tang You,

15:57.960 --> 15:58.760
calm down.

16:00.200 --> 16:02.030
I told you
we shouldn't have brought her along.

16:02.030 --> 16:03.270
But you insisted she was pitiful

16:03.270 --> 16:04.550
and wanted to take her in.

16:04.550 --> 16:05.660
Now look at this mess.

16:05.660 --> 16:07.200
She's caused a huge disaster.

16:07.200 --> 16:08.550
Who's going to
take responsibility for her?

16:08.550 --> 16:08.960
Who?

16:11.030 --> 16:11.960
What are you yelling about?

16:11.960 --> 16:12.840
It's just a painting.

16:12.840 --> 16:13.750
So what if it's sold?

16:13.750 --> 16:14.730
Just a painting?

16:15.320 --> 16:16.390
It's not just a painting.

16:16.390 --> 16:18.450
It's a masterpiece by Master Buquan!

16:18.470 --> 16:19.110
Do you know

16:19.440 --> 16:20.750
how much money and effort

16:20.750 --> 16:21.390
we spent

16:21.390 --> 16:22.600
on that painting?

16:22.840 --> 16:23.600
We came to North Xiang

16:23.600 --> 16:25.000
to handle some important things,

16:25.000 --> 16:26.910
and that painting was the key!

16:27.360 --> 16:28.480
Now it's gone.

16:28.750 --> 16:30.440
Everything we've done is wasted.

16:30.440 --> 16:32.110
What's the point of coming to North Xiang?

16:32.110 --> 16:33.630
Give me back that painting!

16:33.630 --> 16:34.480
Enough.

16:34.670 --> 16:36.240
She didn't sell the painting for herself.

16:36.240 --> 16:37.080
She did it to get money

16:37.080 --> 16:37.890
for Lyu Changyuan's treatment.

16:37.890 --> 16:38.900
Treatment? I...

16:39.480 --> 16:40.000
If I'd known

16:40.000 --> 16:41.360
the painting would be used for treatment,

16:41.360 --> 16:42.360
I would rather...

16:42.390 --> 16:43.920
I would rather kill myself!

16:49.510 --> 16:50.030
Enough.

16:50.050 --> 16:50.550
Alright, alright.

16:50.550 --> 16:51.340
Just let it go.

16:51.340 --> 16:52.200
He's a lunatic.

16:52.200 --> 16:53.460
Why don't you let it go?

16:53.600 --> 16:56.330
You're wrong,
and you're still acting like that.

16:59.840 --> 17:00.770
What do we do now?

17:01.790 --> 17:03.150
All we can do
is to wait for Chen Fen and the others

17:03.150 --> 17:04.410
to come back with news.

17:05.109 --> 17:06.440
One step at a time.

17:21.920 --> 17:22.520
Master Lu.

17:22.920 --> 17:23.650
You're back.

17:32.110 --> 17:32.830
I'm sorry.

17:40.920 --> 17:41.450
Alright.

17:42.020 --> 17:42.640
I, Lord of Rust-Sword,

17:42.640 --> 17:44.310
have traveled far and wide for years.

17:44.310 --> 17:45.310
There's hardly a masterpiece

17:45.310 --> 17:46.590
I haven't laid my eyes on.

17:46.590 --> 17:47.790
When I see...

17:48.350 --> 17:49.950
Master Buquan's paintings,

17:50.120 --> 17:50.960
I'll bring you one.

17:50.960 --> 17:51.820
Simple as that.

17:52.270 --> 17:53.400
That'll be too late.

17:56.200 --> 17:56.800
Zhanying,

17:56.920 --> 17:58.320
did you find that person?

17:59.640 --> 18:00.240
Lu.

18:12.030 --> 18:12.960
Miss Xin.

18:18.680 --> 18:19.880
The teapot is broken.

18:20.000 --> 18:21.130
Hope you don't mind.

18:22.030 --> 18:23.640
Looks like I was too quick

18:23.920 --> 18:25.650
to call you guys frauds before.

18:25.920 --> 18:27.440
You three came from the Central Plains,

18:27.440 --> 18:27.920
acting innocent

18:27.920 --> 18:29.030
the whole way.

18:29.510 --> 18:30.830
Yet you still got all the schools
of the immortal sect

18:30.830 --> 18:32.110
to hunt you down together.

18:32.110 --> 18:33.770
You're obviously organized.

18:34.000 --> 18:35.920
And you've splited into two groups.

18:35.920 --> 18:36.400
Tell me,

18:36.830 --> 18:38.480
what exactly are you here for?

18:38.480 --> 18:40.140
You worry too much, Immortal.

18:40.160 --> 18:42.030
We're just a bunch of ordinary folks.

18:42.030 --> 18:43.310
We're too weak to even tie a chicken.

18:43.310 --> 18:45.040
What could we possibly be up to?

18:46.440 --> 18:47.070
We just

18:47.790 --> 18:50.030
want to copy a few books.

18:50.240 --> 18:51.070
What books?

18:53.070 --> 18:54.670
Unparalleled Secret Magic.

18:55.440 --> 18:57.040
Unparalleled Secret Magic?

19:00.510 --> 19:02.640
There was once a deity in the Human Race

19:02.720 --> 19:04.400
who ascended through Craftsmanship.

19:04.400 --> 19:06.330
She was known as Goddess Wushuang.

19:06.590 --> 19:07.680
She created

19:07.720 --> 19:09.580
many exquisite crafted objects.

19:09.750 --> 19:11.160
For instance, palm-sized houses

19:11.160 --> 19:12.550
that could fit an entire city,

19:12.550 --> 19:13.400
known as Linglong Houses.

19:13.400 --> 19:14.260
And tower ships

19:14.480 --> 19:17.240
that could soar through the sky
without using spiritual power.

19:17.240 --> 19:18.640
There were also cannons, waterwheels,

19:18.640 --> 19:19.680
crossbows, and sharp swords.

19:19.680 --> 19:21.210
They were all fine weapons.

19:21.720 --> 19:22.680
Sir,

19:23.000 --> 19:24.660
you're quite knowledgeable.

19:24.790 --> 19:25.720
Sir, may I ask,

19:26.270 --> 19:28.270
are you also from the immortal sect?

19:29.400 --> 19:30.860
I don't belong to any side.

19:33.070 --> 19:34.800
You've told me all this before,

19:35.240 --> 19:36.970
but it doesn't prove anything.

19:40.000 --> 19:41.800
Immortal, you don't believe me?

19:43.070 --> 19:43.830
Immortal,

19:44.160 --> 19:45.240
you're a good person,

19:45.240 --> 19:47.140
but also very stubborn.

19:47.720 --> 19:49.450
If I don't tell the truth today,

19:49.640 --> 19:51.300
I'm afraid you won't let it go.

19:51.590 --> 19:52.590
In that case,

19:54.000 --> 19:55.330
I'll be honest with you.

19:58.110 --> 19:58.680
We

20:00.110 --> 20:02.040
are all from the Wushuang Society.

20:06.310 --> 20:07.270
The Wushuang Society

20:07.270 --> 20:10.030
is an organization formed spontaneously
by the Human Race.

20:10.030 --> 20:10.790
Its purpose

20:11.130 --> 20:12.640
is to restore Goddess Wushuang's

20:12.640 --> 20:13.640
Craftsmanship

20:14.680 --> 20:16.880
and find a new path

20:16.880 --> 20:17.960
for the Human Race.

20:18.960 --> 20:20.420
Over a thousand years ago,

20:20.830 --> 20:22.000
Craftsmanship

20:22.240 --> 20:24.200
spread among the Human Race.

20:25.960 --> 20:27.490
At that time, the Human Race

20:27.680 --> 20:29.920
could possess power

20:30.400 --> 20:31.590
comparable to an god

20:32.070 --> 20:33.440
simply by learning Craftsmanship.

20:33.440 --> 20:35.830
No need for the help
of immortal perception.

20:35.830 --> 20:37.490
If such power really existed,

20:37.880 --> 20:39.410
why has it disappeared now?

20:40.750 --> 20:41.590
About that...

20:42.680 --> 20:44.680
you'd have to ask the immortal sect.

20:44.680 --> 20:45.550
The immortal sect?

20:45.550 --> 20:46.610
Sir, don't you know

20:46.920 --> 20:49.050
that it's precisely the immortal sect

20:49.160 --> 20:51.480
that protects and blesses the Human Race?

20:51.480 --> 20:53.000
Deities bless the people

20:53.400 --> 20:54.920
but expect incense offerings.

20:54.920 --> 20:56.580
Dynasties protect the people

20:56.680 --> 20:58.000
but expect taxes.

20:58.480 --> 20:59.830
The immortal sect is the same.

20:59.830 --> 21:01.760
There's no free lunch in the world.

21:02.790 --> 21:03.550
However,

21:03.960 --> 21:05.550
when the Human Race became so powerful

21:05.550 --> 21:06.640
that it rivaled

21:07.200 --> 21:08.920
the immortal sect,

21:09.510 --> 21:10.440
would the immortal sect

21:10.440 --> 21:12.300
still be willing to protect them?

21:15.720 --> 21:17.180
It seemed that overnight,

21:18.070 --> 21:20.000
all the techniques of Craftsmanship

21:20.000 --> 21:21.200
were destroyed,

21:22.000 --> 21:23.690
and the ancient texts vanished.

21:23.690 --> 21:25.410
The craftsmen and scholars

21:25.440 --> 21:26.720
who held that knowledge

21:26.720 --> 21:27.980
were all perished too.

21:28.720 --> 21:30.270
The strike came like thunder,

21:30.270 --> 21:32.310
too powerful for the Human Race
to withstand.

21:32.310 --> 21:35.170
The civilization and technology
of the Human Race,

21:35.310 --> 21:36.350
were wiped out

21:37.680 --> 21:39.440
in the blink of an eye.

21:45.750 --> 21:47.750
Therefore, a thousand years later,

21:49.310 --> 21:50.570
we came to North Xiang.

21:54.310 --> 21:55.640
In ancient times,

21:57.000 --> 21:59.680
a great monk traveled west for a scripture

22:00.640 --> 22:03.070
and brought blessings to the Human Race.

22:04.480 --> 22:06.510
We're here for a scripture too.

22:08.270 --> 22:09.330
A sacred scripture

22:10.070 --> 22:12.350
that can benefit the Human Race.

22:14.960 --> 22:16.690
The powers of the immortal sect

22:16.790 --> 22:18.480
can indeed help some people

22:18.680 --> 22:20.590
awaken their immortal perception

22:20.590 --> 22:21.350
and possess powers

22:21.350 --> 22:22.750
beyond ordinary people.

22:23.790 --> 22:25.310
But for ordinary people,

22:25.480 --> 22:26.920
it's a disaster.

22:28.110 --> 22:29.550
The gap between them

22:29.920 --> 22:31.580
is getting bigger and bigger.

22:31.750 --> 22:33.830
No matter how hard the ordinary people
work in their lifetime,

22:33.830 --> 22:35.830
they can never cross that high wall.

22:38.110 --> 22:38.830
Perhaps,

22:40.920 --> 22:43.030
the moment cultivators awaken

22:43.030 --> 22:44.630
their immortal perception,

22:46.160 --> 22:48.220
they're already a different species

22:48.270 --> 22:49.830
from the Human Race.

22:50.440 --> 22:51.640
A different species?

22:53.030 --> 22:54.160
Aren't cultivators

22:54.240 --> 22:54.680
still a part

22:54.680 --> 22:56.200
of the people?

22:57.000 --> 22:59.680
Sure, cultivators have the power
strong enough to destroy mountains.

22:59.680 --> 23:00.160
But don't the masters

23:00.160 --> 23:01.750
from the martial world

23:02.160 --> 23:03.420
have strong power too?

23:03.790 --> 23:04.700
In my opinion,

23:04.920 --> 23:06.550
the common people live in cities,

23:06.550 --> 23:07.920
and immortals live in forests.

23:07.920 --> 23:08.850
Other than that,

23:08.880 --> 23:10.210
there's no difference.

23:10.350 --> 23:12.270
That's just your opinion, Immortal.

23:12.270 --> 23:13.270
Can you guarantee

23:13.680 --> 23:14.920
that every member of the immortal sect

23:14.920 --> 23:16.400
thinks the same way as you?

23:16.840 --> 23:17.480
We don't have

23:17.480 --> 23:19.110
the power to summon wind and rain,

23:19.110 --> 23:21.510
so we have to find our own way.

23:21.750 --> 23:23.080
We invented irrigation

23:23.440 --> 23:25.240
to assist in farming.

23:25.550 --> 23:27.110
With Astronomy and Calendar,

23:27.110 --> 23:27.830
we can tell

23:27.830 --> 23:28.700
when the wind will blow

23:28.700 --> 23:30.230
and when the rain will fall.

23:30.480 --> 23:32.410
Arithmetic enlightens our minds.

23:32.550 --> 23:34.830
Poetry and painting build our characters.

23:34.830 --> 23:35.790
And Craftsmanship

23:35.790 --> 23:37.110
is the most

23:37.160 --> 23:38.160
practical skill.

23:38.510 --> 23:41.000
It allows us to fly and burrow,

23:41.270 --> 23:42.350
and live

23:42.750 --> 23:43.720
a more ideal

23:44.200 --> 23:45.510
and convenient life.

23:46.590 --> 23:47.920
Compared to practicing immortal arts,

23:47.920 --> 23:48.960
this is the path

23:49.510 --> 23:51.070
the Human Race should take.

23:51.590 --> 23:52.400
Therefore,

23:53.270 --> 23:55.730
we must bring
the Unparalleled Secret Magic

23:56.110 --> 23:57.640
back to the Central Plains.

23:58.790 --> 23:59.790
The Unparalleled Secret Magic

23:59.790 --> 24:01.400
originally had 46 volumes,

24:01.790 --> 24:04.120
all written by Goddess Wushuang herself.

24:04.830 --> 24:06.510
Later, many craftsmen

24:06.510 --> 24:07.680
were inspired by it

24:08.030 --> 24:09.240
and created many

24:09.270 --> 24:10.550
wonderful inventions,

24:10.550 --> 24:12.000
which were all added

24:12.200 --> 24:14.130
to the Unparalleled Secret Magic.

24:14.310 --> 24:16.230
Astronomy, Calendar, Arithmetic,

24:16.230 --> 24:17.510
Craftsmanship, and Poetry

24:17.510 --> 24:18.920
are all recorded in it.

24:19.200 --> 24:21.510
In total, it now consists of 120 volumes.

24:22.400 --> 24:23.720
But the ancient texts
in the Central Plains

24:23.720 --> 24:24.720
have long been lost,

24:24.720 --> 24:27.920
and the Unparalleled Secret Magic
is nowhere to be found.

24:28.030 --> 24:30.000
The only remaining copy is kept

24:30.000 --> 24:32.730
in the Sihe Library
in Phoenix City, North Xiang.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.100
It could be said

24:34.480 --> 24:35.920
that thousands of years

24:36.270 --> 24:37.750
of the Human Race's wisdom and heritage

24:37.750 --> 24:39.480
are all contained in this book.

24:39.920 --> 24:40.850
Unfortunately,

24:41.000 --> 24:42.200
the Sihe Library

24:42.200 --> 24:43.200
has strict rules.

24:44.000 --> 24:46.530
No paper or writing tools
are allowed inside.

24:46.680 --> 24:47.790
You can only read.

24:48.070 --> 24:49.920
And it opens only once every five years,

24:49.920 --> 24:51.440
for just ten days.

24:52.480 --> 24:53.590
It's also very hard

24:55.000 --> 24:56.160
to get in.

24:57.680 --> 24:58.270
Hard?

24:59.270 --> 25:01.200
If you want to read the books there,

25:01.330 --> 25:02.860
you have to trade something

25:02.880 --> 25:03.680
of equal value.

25:03.680 --> 25:05.550
They only accept books and paintings.

25:05.550 --> 25:06.810
Even money won't work!

25:07.400 --> 25:09.510
The painting, Pair of Wild Geese,

25:09.590 --> 25:11.160
was the key to our entry.

25:11.590 --> 25:13.400
But now, An has sold it.

25:13.880 --> 25:15.790
And we can't find the buyer
to get it back.

25:15.790 --> 25:17.320
The opening is almost here.

25:17.440 --> 25:19.720
If we don't get in now, it'll be too late.

25:21.040 --> 25:21.790
The Unparalleled Secret Magic

25:21.790 --> 25:22.790
has 120 volumes.

25:23.400 --> 25:24.330
Even if we get in,

25:24.590 --> 25:26.160
there's no way to learn it all.

25:26.160 --> 25:27.560
But we still have to go in!

25:27.820 --> 25:28.510
After all,

25:28.830 --> 25:30.490
we may not get another chance!

25:31.400 --> 25:33.350
We split into three groups this time.

25:33.350 --> 25:34.880
There were 36 of us in total.

25:34.920 --> 25:36.480
One group was ambushed,

25:37.000 --> 25:38.240
leaving only twenty.

25:38.680 --> 25:39.720
And I'm not sure

25:40.030 --> 25:41.830
if these twenty will make it back

25:42.240 --> 25:43.500
to the Central Plains.

25:45.550 --> 25:46.810
Is there any other way?

25:48.350 --> 25:49.310
Right and wrong

25:49.590 --> 25:51.410
can't be settled just by arguing.

25:51.410 --> 25:52.200
Actually, there are many things

25:52.200 --> 25:53.260
I can't figure out.

25:53.590 --> 25:55.070
But if we just stay here,

25:55.590 --> 25:57.160
we'll never figure them out.

25:57.160 --> 25:59.020
So let's take a bold step forward.

25:59.090 --> 26:00.040
Maybe we'll discover

26:00.040 --> 26:00.900
something new.

26:01.620 --> 26:02.580
If you need it,

26:02.720 --> 26:03.480
I can help.

26:04.070 --> 26:06.160
Maybe the only way to settle all arguments

26:06.160 --> 26:07.690
is to get inside the library

26:07.830 --> 26:09.400
and see the sacred scripture

26:09.400 --> 26:10.400
with our own eyes.

26:10.830 --> 26:11.750
That painting

26:12.830 --> 26:14.400
is a masterpiece by Wu Buquan,

26:14.400 --> 26:16.270
who's also known as Master Buquan.

26:16.270 --> 26:17.640
In his early years,

26:17.830 --> 26:19.030
he taught at the Imperial Palace.

26:19.030 --> 26:21.090
He was the current emperor's mentor.

26:21.440 --> 26:22.770
That ink painting of his

26:22.830 --> 26:24.070
is unmatched in this era.

26:24.070 --> 26:26.440
His brushstrokes are bold,
and his energy flows like the wind.

26:26.440 --> 26:28.830
He's the greatest ink painter of all time.

26:29.310 --> 26:31.590
But his works are rarely seen.

26:32.640 --> 26:33.300
Most of them

26:33.510 --> 26:34.750
have been collected by Emperor Zong Ding

26:34.750 --> 26:36.680
and kept in the imperial treasury.

26:36.750 --> 26:39.110
Only a few pieces have made it
to the outside world.

26:39.110 --> 26:41.590
But they cost a fortune.

26:43.550 --> 26:44.710
It's impossible

26:45.070 --> 26:46.510
to find a replacement

26:47.510 --> 26:49.480
in just a few days.

26:53.110 --> 26:54.640
I happen to have a few pieces

26:55.440 --> 26:57.350
by Wu Buquan, the Master Painter.

26:59.270 --> 27:00.920
Sir, is that true?

27:01.350 --> 27:02.080
To be honest,

27:02.510 --> 27:03.920
I love collecting paintings

27:03.920 --> 27:05.000
by famous masters.

27:05.550 --> 27:06.510
When I was traveling

27:06.510 --> 27:08.200
in the capital,

27:08.480 --> 27:09.740
I happened to buy three

27:09.830 --> 27:10.630
at a pawnshop.

27:10.920 --> 27:12.030
Master Buquan has painted

27:12.030 --> 27:14.030
only about fifty pieces in his life.

27:14.070 --> 27:15.240
Each one has a title

27:15.270 --> 27:16.030
and a date.

27:17.350 --> 27:18.680
Which three did you buy?

27:20.350 --> 27:21.680
One is Luoxi Landscape,

27:21.830 --> 27:23.480
one is White Cranes Flying South,

27:23.480 --> 27:25.940
and the last
is Sunset on an Autumn Sandbank.

27:26.240 --> 27:27.640
Isn't Luoxi Landscape

27:28.270 --> 27:30.530
supposed to be in the imperial treasury?

27:30.550 --> 27:31.590
And I've never

27:31.920 --> 27:33.270
heard of the other two.

27:34.240 --> 27:35.920
The one in the treasury
is the horizontal version.

27:35.920 --> 27:37.120
Mine is the vertical.

27:38.070 --> 27:39.270
There's such a thing?

27:40.920 --> 27:42.350
Anyway, I'll deliver the painting

27:42.350 --> 27:43.610
at this time tomorrow.

27:43.920 --> 27:45.000
Whether it's true or not,

27:45.000 --> 27:45.860
we'll find out.

27:58.400 --> 27:59.200
Do you think

27:59.480 --> 28:01.010
they're telling the truth?

28:03.480 --> 28:04.960
You're neither from the immortal sect

28:04.960 --> 28:06.020
nor the Human Race.

28:06.480 --> 28:08.310
You've lived a long life and seen a lot.

28:08.310 --> 28:09.840
I want your honest opinion.

28:12.350 --> 28:13.410
At a time like this,

28:13.680 --> 28:14.270
whatever I say

28:14.270 --> 28:15.800
will affect your judgment.

28:16.070 --> 28:17.870
It's better not to say anything.

28:18.400 --> 28:19.860
I don't believe it anyway.

28:19.960 --> 28:20.750
I can't just take

28:20.750 --> 28:22.080
their one-sided story.

28:22.270 --> 28:23.880
Besides, they're scammers.

28:24.240 --> 28:25.830
They stole the secret manual
of Lingji Mountain

28:25.830 --> 28:26.590
and my money.

28:26.920 --> 28:28.310
They also cheated the common people
of their money

28:28.310 --> 28:29.240
and blamed everything

28:29.240 --> 28:30.440
on the immortal sect,

28:30.720 --> 28:32.250
washing their hands clean.

28:36.640 --> 28:38.040
What are you laughing at?

28:39.070 --> 28:40.410
Since you think that way,

28:40.410 --> 28:40.960
why don't you

28:40.960 --> 28:42.070
just capture them

28:42.310 --> 28:44.510
and hand them over to the immortal sect?

28:45.510 --> 28:47.720
The road is beneath my feet,
and the path is in my heart.

28:47.720 --> 28:48.980
I need to walk further.

28:49.400 --> 28:51.530
I haven't figured everything out yet.

28:52.000 --> 28:52.530
However,

28:52.650 --> 28:53.680
you still have to give them the painting

28:53.680 --> 28:54.480
you promised.

28:54.510 --> 28:56.170
You can't go back on your word.

28:56.270 --> 28:56.870
Of course.

28:57.960 --> 28:59.510
Then where do we get it?

29:00.880 --> 29:01.540
Here we are.

29:07.400 --> 29:08.800
What can I get for you two?

29:09.720 --> 29:10.790
Brush, ink, paper, and inkstone.

29:10.570 --> 29:12.880
[Zhiyan Studio]

29:11.000 --> 29:11.440
Okay.

29:11.750 --> 29:13.010
Just a moment, please.

29:22.350 --> 29:23.510
Your method

29:24.030 --> 29:25.630
is just to paint it yourself?

29:26.110 --> 29:26.680
Yes.

29:27.240 --> 29:28.300
Are you forging it?

29:30.030 --> 29:31.350
How is this forging?

29:35.270 --> 29:36.530
Come and grind the ink.

29:57.200 --> 29:58.480
In my early years of painting,

29:58.480 --> 30:00.400
I preferred sharp, bold brushstrokes.

30:00.400 --> 30:01.680
I drew towering peaks and jagged cliffs,

30:01.680 --> 30:03.410
along with trickling streams.

30:03.550 --> 30:03.960
Later,

30:04.240 --> 30:05.700
I left the Imperial Palace

30:06.110 --> 30:08.110
and could no longer use this identity.

30:08.110 --> 30:09.680
So I changed my painting style.

30:09.680 --> 30:11.000
My brushstrokes became softer,

30:11.000 --> 30:12.260
and the touch lighter,

30:12.590 --> 30:13.920
focusing on the contrast

30:13.920 --> 30:15.320
between black and white.

30:16.200 --> 30:17.200
The paintings you saw

30:17.200 --> 30:17.930
in Wei County

30:18.400 --> 30:19.070
were all done

30:19.070 --> 30:20.470
after I changed my style.

30:20.880 --> 30:21.640
Smoother,

30:22.160 --> 30:23.160
but lacking edge.

30:23.830 --> 30:24.750
What I like most

30:25.270 --> 30:27.530
are still the sharp, bold brushstrokes.

30:28.350 --> 30:30.590
Master Buquan, Wu Buquan...

30:31.110 --> 30:31.920
That's you?

30:36.550 --> 30:37.920
How many other identities do you have

30:37.920 --> 30:39.250
that I don't know about?

30:43.790 --> 30:46.920
The wind and mist are gone.
The sky and mountains share one hue.

30:46.920 --> 30:48.000
The sun is setting,

30:48.790 --> 30:50.790
leaving behind a wisp of afterglow.

30:52.680 --> 30:53.920
Now I finally understand

30:53.920 --> 30:55.780
why the ticket to the Sihe Library

30:56.240 --> 30:57.680
had to be your painting.

31:01.360 --> 31:03.070
Isn't it a pity for the afterglow

31:03.070 --> 31:05.030
to miss the final touch?

31:32.720 --> 31:33.240
Done.

32:02.000 --> 32:02.800
You're awake?

32:05.400 --> 32:05.790
Here.

32:06.880 --> 32:07.610
Take it easy.

32:09.640 --> 32:10.480
You saved me.

32:11.590 --> 32:13.250
Why are you in North Xiang too?

32:14.680 --> 32:16.510
I came here with some other disciples
from the immortal sect

32:16.510 --> 32:17.770
to handle a few things.

32:18.210 --> 32:18.790
Right after I met with Jiang Ji

32:18.790 --> 32:19.920
and Nangong Guhong,

32:20.400 --> 32:22.110
I heard something had happened to you,

32:22.110 --> 32:23.240
so I came to find you.

32:24.920 --> 32:25.790
Where are we?

32:27.790 --> 32:28.640
In a cave.

32:29.680 --> 32:30.610
When I found you,

32:30.830 --> 32:32.430
you were already unconscious.

32:32.430 --> 32:34.480
Half of your body was buried in the sand,

32:34.480 --> 32:35.880
and you were losing heat.

32:36.550 --> 32:37.840
I was afraid you might get worse,

32:37.840 --> 32:38.560
so I took you

32:38.590 --> 32:40.270
to the nearest place for treatment.

32:40.270 --> 32:41.730
How far is the nearest city

32:41.750 --> 32:42.720
in the Central Plains from here?

32:42.720 --> 32:44.720
You want to go to the Central Plains?

32:46.560 --> 32:47.680
Lingji Mountain and Sun Moon Cavern

32:47.680 --> 32:49.270
have sent many disciples
to look after you.

32:49.270 --> 32:50.530
If you enter a city now,

32:50.830 --> 32:52.230
you'll be an easy target.

32:54.440 --> 32:55.160
Well,

32:56.720 --> 32:58.160
the wound on your shoulder...

32:58.160 --> 32:59.270
If you don't mind,

33:00.110 --> 33:01.640
I'll take care of it for you.

33:18.680 --> 33:19.740
It might hurt a bit.

33:19.790 --> 33:20.790
Just bear with me.

34:06.030 --> 34:07.490
Didn't you just see it all?

34:07.790 --> 34:08.850
I was saving a life.

34:09.320 --> 34:11.360
To a healer, there is no difference
between men and women.

34:11.360 --> 34:11.909
But now...

34:11.909 --> 34:12.429
Now,

34:12.710 --> 34:13.670
why did you stop?

34:14.230 --> 34:15.000
Now what?

34:16.070 --> 34:17.320
Why did you stop now?

34:28.230 --> 34:29.280
This is Tianyin Mountain's

34:29.280 --> 34:31.340
Infinite Heart Purification Spell.

34:31.510 --> 34:32.429
I've heard

34:33.070 --> 34:35.510
Tianyin Mountain forbids desires and lust.

34:35.510 --> 34:37.110
Whenever someone
is about to cross the line,

34:37.110 --> 34:39.440
they use spells to clear their minds

34:39.960 --> 34:41.420
and restrain themselves.

34:42.920 --> 34:43.440
What?

34:44.320 --> 34:46.050
Are you about to cross the line?

34:53.670 --> 34:54.320
Fine.

34:54.800 --> 34:56.060
I'll stop teasing you.

34:58.110 --> 34:58.960
What was that golden lotus

34:58.960 --> 35:00.190
you used to heal me?

35:01.150 --> 35:03.070
Is it a Tianyin Mountain divine artifact,

35:03.070 --> 35:04.320
like your bracelet?

35:13.070 --> 35:13.870
You mean this?

35:14.760 --> 35:15.960
Yes, that's the one.

35:17.070 --> 35:18.530
I told you about it before.

35:18.960 --> 35:19.960
I don't remember.

35:20.630 --> 35:22.110
It transformed from
the golden lotus in the pond

35:22.110 --> 35:24.170
and then flew right between my brows.

35:26.320 --> 35:28.070
You were born on September 9th,

35:28.760 --> 35:30.290
and you bear a golden lotus.

35:30.800 --> 35:31.550
Maybe

35:31.920 --> 35:33.780
you really are the compassionate

35:33.840 --> 35:35.710
and merciful savior of the world.

35:38.630 --> 35:39.150
Weren't you also

35:39.150 --> 35:40.410
born on September 9th?

35:43.030 --> 35:43.960
How did you know?

35:45.150 --> 35:45.760
I guessed.

35:47.000 --> 35:47.860
You tricked me.

35:51.590 --> 35:52.440
So do you think

35:53.360 --> 35:54.690
you could be the savior?

35:55.480 --> 35:57.000
It could be anyone, but not me.

35:57.000 --> 35:57.510
Why?

35:58.840 --> 36:00.500
Because I'm not a good person.

36:00.770 --> 36:02.900
I have no interest in saving the world.

36:03.670 --> 36:04.710
I just want to go back

36:04.710 --> 36:06.440
to Xin Xie Manor with my senior sister

36:06.440 --> 36:07.800
and live a quiet life.

36:08.450 --> 36:09.980
You're good to your senior.

36:10.360 --> 36:12.020
She's the one who's good to me.

36:12.960 --> 36:14.320
She's the only person in this world

36:14.320 --> 36:15.920
who's truly sincere with me.

36:17.000 --> 36:17.730
Besides her,

36:18.110 --> 36:19.240
there's no one else.

36:19.630 --> 36:20.960
And there never will be.

36:21.710 --> 36:22.970
I'll be good to you too.

36:24.070 --> 36:25.030
I told you.

36:25.960 --> 36:27.510
I've got cold blood, cold lungs,

36:27.510 --> 36:28.240
a cold heart.

36:28.920 --> 36:30.050
Nothing can warm me.

36:30.400 --> 36:32.280
Don't think that
just because you saved me,

36:32.280 --> 36:33.710
I'll be grateful to you.

36:36.800 --> 36:38.000
Why are you laughing?

36:39.360 --> 36:40.320
My master once told me

36:40.320 --> 36:40.920
a story.

36:42.320 --> 36:44.030
In the forest of Tianyin Mountain,

36:44.030 --> 36:45.230
there was a hedgehog.

36:46.400 --> 36:47.000
One day,

36:47.480 --> 36:48.070
its belly

36:48.070 --> 36:49.600
got cut by poisonous grass.

36:49.920 --> 36:51.440
My master tried to heal it,

36:52.510 --> 36:53.480
but it was so scared

36:53.480 --> 36:54.440
that it curled up tightly.

36:54.440 --> 36:55.640
Eventually, it died.

36:57.030 --> 36:57.920
My master said

36:58.800 --> 36:59.960
its spikes

37:00.590 --> 37:02.150
were a protective shield,

37:03.000 --> 37:04.530
but also an isolating wall.

37:04.920 --> 37:06.320
When one curls up inside,

37:06.760 --> 37:08.440
it's hard to see
what's truly in his heart.

37:08.440 --> 37:10.670
Sounds like you're subtly criticizing me.

37:10.670 --> 37:11.600
I wouldn't dare.

37:33.190 --> 37:35.110
When we just got here, it was night.

37:35.110 --> 37:36.200
Pitch-black.

37:36.280 --> 37:37.540
I couldn't see a thing.

37:39.510 --> 37:40.550
I didn't expect the scenery here

37:40.550 --> 37:41.750
to be this beautiful.

37:45.280 --> 37:46.150
Where are we?

37:48.000 --> 37:48.800
What's wrong?

37:49.000 --> 37:49.840
Where are we?

37:51.710 --> 37:52.630
On my way here,

37:52.920 --> 37:54.520
I ran into an old woodcutter.

37:54.800 --> 37:57.130
He said this place is called Qianyan Cave.

37:57.800 --> 37:59.280
It was carved out
through countless hardships,

37:59.280 --> 38:00.630
scorched by raging fire,

38:00.630 --> 38:02.320
and finally chiseled into a cave.

38:02.320 --> 38:03.780
It's actually a good name.

38:22.920 --> 38:24.050
It's the real thing.

38:24.200 --> 38:25.550
It's really a masterpiece

38:25.550 --> 38:26.550
by Master Buquan!

38:26.860 --> 38:28.710
Lu is the number one martial hero
in the martial world.

38:28.710 --> 38:30.300
Every word he says is rock solid.

38:30.300 --> 38:31.360
He would never lie to you.

38:31.360 --> 38:32.090
Awesome, Lu!

38:33.510 --> 38:34.230
These two

38:34.400 --> 38:36.400
are genuine works of Master Buquan.

38:38.280 --> 38:39.210
That one is fake.

38:39.480 --> 38:40.590
How's that possible?

38:40.590 --> 38:41.670
Take a closer look.

38:42.150 --> 38:43.150
It can't be wrong.

38:43.400 --> 38:45.070
Immortal Xin, you may not have noticed,

38:45.070 --> 38:46.550
but when Master Buquan paints,

38:46.550 --> 38:48.590
he only uses thick ink,
just black and white.

38:48.590 --> 38:50.320
He never uses any other colors.

38:50.840 --> 38:52.480
So this painting of sunset

38:52.800 --> 38:53.800
must be fake.

38:57.440 --> 38:59.320
If you don't want it, I'll keep it.

39:01.400 --> 39:02.000
Master Lu.

39:02.670 --> 39:04.150
Master Buquan's masterpiece

39:04.150 --> 39:05.550
is worth a thousand gold.

39:05.610 --> 39:06.960
But we've spent all our travel money

39:06.960 --> 39:08.000
on the way here.

39:08.280 --> 39:10.010
We have nothing valuable on us,

39:10.230 --> 39:11.800
only a few copper coins left.

39:11.800 --> 39:13.600
We were planning to buy some food

39:13.660 --> 39:15.510
later to eat in the library.

39:16.360 --> 39:18.440
I guess you wouldn't want them anyway.

39:18.440 --> 39:19.370
No need to pay me.

39:19.660 --> 39:21.660
These paintings are my gifts to you.

39:22.590 --> 39:23.790
Well, look at that...

39:24.190 --> 39:25.550
Can you be any more fake?

39:28.150 --> 39:29.680
On behalf of the Human Race,

39:30.390 --> 39:31.590
thank you, Master Lu!

39:36.070 --> 39:36.760
How about

39:36.960 --> 39:38.760
we treat you to a meal, Master Lu?

39:42.710 --> 39:45.150
No need to go through the trouble.

39:45.320 --> 39:45.800
No way!

39:46.320 --> 39:48.450
A gentleman always returns kindness.

39:49.420 --> 39:50.550
Master Lu, please wait a moment.

39:50.550 --> 39:52.010
The food will be here soon.

39:52.110 --> 39:52.640
Let's go.

39:53.080 --> 39:53.360
Okay.

39:53.360 --> 39:53.890
Let's go.

39:54.550 --> 39:55.360
Let's go.

39:55.590 --> 39:56.110
Hurry.

39:59.480 --> 40:00.010
Let's go.

40:00.590 --> 40:01.000
Let's go.
